data.description: You won't find another property out there like this one. STUNNING 4 bedroom, 4 Bath home with 3,441sq ft of living space with a fully finished basement. Unique build that has been well maintained. First floor Primary. Complimenting this beautiful home is a spectacularly landscaped yard. Featuring this home is a rock fountain, cozy shed including water and electric, aluminum fence, and perennial garden. First floor houses a very open floor concept with beautiful high ceilings. The kitchen and breakfast area provides a panoramic view of the outside. Many will appreciate the first-floor master with a relaxing bath and plenty of closet space. The office includes daylight windows, downstairs could be used as a 4th bedroom. Upstairs nestles two bedrooms that is joined by a jack and jill style bathroom. Also including a comfortable loft area. Please don't skip over the noteworthy 3 car garage.
